=================================================================
  IMPORTANT CAVEATS
=================================================================

  1. n = 7–8 books. BERT has 105M parameters. Overfitting
     trivially possible. Embedding distances are a RELATIVE
     cross-check, not an independent authorship claim.

  2. Latin BERT was pretrained on heterogeneous Latin corpora.
     Domain shift from Caesar's military prose is unquantified.

  3. Contextual embeddings capture semantics + syntax + genre.
     Unlike function-word Delta, we cannot separate 'style'
     from 'content' in embedding space.

  4. The agreement (or disagreement) between classical stylometry
     and embedding distances is INFORMATIVE but should not be
     treated as a weighted vote. Methods differ fundamentally.

